snippet.title: Vault: Tomb of the King - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
ITCH.IO - https://vaulttotk.itch.io/vault-tomb-of-the-king

GAME JOLT - https://gamejolt.com/games/Vault/389165

https://www.BraveTheVault.com

Vault is an action-puzzle dungeon crawler. Swap between the Fighter the Thief and the Wizard to overcome deadly enemies and traps.
